➜Chinese Elite Seascape BWMS approved by USCG
http://www.sohu.com/a/425417405_624484	57153
<p>On October 16, 2020, the United States Coast Guard (USCG) maritime certification body, issued its approval certificate to Chinese Elite Seascape ballast water management system (BWMS), which means Elite could provide the ballast water management system that meets maritime requirements for ships sailing worldwide. It is estimated that in the future, more than 30,000 ships haveto install ballast water management systems from qualified BWMS makers.</p>
<p>We at International Ship &amp; Offshore Media China would like to offer our warm congratulations to Elite Seascape BWMS team, who has been actively taking part in our industry-specific forums and will come again on Dec.2-4, 2020 in Shanghai for 5th Marine BWMS &amp; Scrubber Shanghai Int'l Summit 2020 in conjunction with Green Intelligent Ship &amp; Offshore Shanghai Conference 2020</p>
<p>http://www.ishipoffshore.com/html/11/2020-04-08/10727.htm</p>
<p><a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/423867429_624484 " target="_blank">免费的第五届船用压载水系统BWMS和洗涤塔上海2020年峰会将于12月4日举办</a></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201017/36c9fa31526d44f1aea1574addfb89b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201017/5ff06675ddb44b67937ec19d02714df7.png" max-width="600" /></p>